OL,3,CGermany to vote on legalising cannabis
OL,4,Cbut under strict regulations
OL,6,FGerman politicians are to vote on
OL,7,Fwhether to decriminalise limited
OL,8,Famounts of marijuana and allow members
OL,9,Fof so-called "cannabis clubs" to buy
OL,10,Fit for recreational purposes.
OL,12,FBut this does not mean anyone can
OL,13,Fsmoke, use or sell unlimited amounts
OL,14,Fof marijuana anywhere in Germany -
OL,15,Fthere are strict rules.
OL,17,FThe bill will legalise possession of
OL,18,Fup to 25 grams of marijuana for
OL,19,Frecreational purposes for over 18s and
OL,20,Fallow individuals to grow up to three
OL,21,Fplants on their own.
