OL,3,CGermany to vote on legalising cannabis
OL,4,Cbut under strict regulations
OL,6,FThat part of the legislation would
OL,7,Ftake effect on April 1.
OL,9,FHowever, people would not be allowed
OL,10,Fto use cannabis within 200 metres of
OL,11,Fschools, playgrounds and sports
OL,12,Ffacilities, or near cannabis clubs.
OL,14,FAn evaluation of the legislation's
OL,15,Feffect on protection of children and
OL,16,Fyoung people will be carried out
OL,17,Fwithin 18 months of the law coming
OL,18,Finto force.
