OL,3,CGermany to vote on legalising cannabis
OL,4,Cbut under strict regulations
OL,6,FGerman residents, who are 18 and
OL,7,Folder, are to be allowed to join
OL,8,Fnonprofit "cannabis clubs" with a
OL,9,Fmaximum 500 members each, starting on
OL,10,FJuly 1.
OL,12,FEach person can only join one club,
OL,13,Fand the costs would be covered by
OL,14,Fmembership fees, which would be
OL,15,Fstaggered according to how much
OL,16,Fmarijuana members use.
OL,18,FThe clubs will be allowed to grow
OL,19,Fcannabis for members' personal
OL,20,Fconsumption.
