OL,3,CGermany to vote on legalising cannabis
OL,4,Cbut under strict regulations
OL,6,FAdvertising or sponsoring the drug at
OL,7,Fthe clubs will be banned by the
OL,8,Fgovernment.
OL,10,FThe new relaxed policy is to be
OL,11,Faccompanied by a campaign to warn
OL,12,Fyoung people of the risks of consuming
OL,13,Fthe drug.
OL,15,FThis is just the first stage of
OL,16,FGermany's cannabis plan, the second
OL,17,Fpart would see a five-year trial of
OL,18,Fregulated commercial supply chains in
OL,19,Fparts of the county, it was reported
OL,20,Fin August.
