OL,6,FThese would then be scientifically
OL,7,Fevaluated.
OL,9,FThe plan falls significantly short of
OL,10,Fthe government's original ambitions,
OL,11,Fwhich would have allowed the sale of
OL,12,Fcannabis to adults across the country
OL,13,Fat licensed outlets.
OL,15,FThe project was scaled back after
OL,16,Ftalks with the European Union's
OL,17,Fexecutive commission.
