OL,7,Fmonths after Chancellor Olaf Scholz's
OL,8,FCabinet gave its blessing to the plan,
OL,9,Fa prominent reform project of the
OL,10,Fsocially liberal governing coalition.
OL,12,FGermany's main conservative opposition
OL,13,Fparty have always been against the
OL,14,Fmore liberal proposals as have some
OL,15,Fmembers of Scholz's centre-left Social
OL,16,FDemocrats.
